<section id="ctr_datetime">
  <title>ctr_datetime</title>

  <para>Date and Time, datetime - Indicates the date and time the referenced element or its
    attributes were created or modified.</para>

  <para><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><emphasis>Type:</emphasis>
    string.<?oxy_custom_end?></para>
  <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> Date in one of the formats defined in <olink
      targetdoc="../../xliff21.xml" targetptr="bib_datetime">[NOTE-datetime]</olink>.</para>

  <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> undefined.</para>

  <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis><olink targetdoc="../../elements/change-tracking/revision.xml"
      targetptr="revision"><code>ctr_revision</code></olink>.</para>
  
</section>
